dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Ancillary maps: Guadalajara, Jal.--Monterrey, N.L.--León, Gto.--Puebla, Pue.--Acapulco, Gro. IncludesTourist information and "Program of the games of the XIX Olympiad". Map on verso includes an inset of Mexico City region, tourist information, index, distance chart, "Approximate driving time" diagram. Shows location of Olympic Games. "Derechos reservados © por el Gobierno Federal de los Estados Unidos Mexicanos".
